<problem id="fs-id1163975531667">
<para id="fs-id1163974219597">Describe at least two characteristics of the universe that are explained by the standard Big Bang model.</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1163975394577">
<problem id="fs-id1163974318299">
<para id="fs-id1163975545327">Describe two properties of the universe that are not explained by the standard Big Bang model (without inflation). How does inflation explain these two properties?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
