</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1163976539387">
<problem id="fs-id1163976458316">
<para id="fs-id1163976766205">Thinking about the ideas of space and time in Einstein’s general theory of relativity, how do we explain the fact that all galaxies outside our Local Group show a redshift?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-id1163976748132">
<problem id="fs-id1163976407982">
